# Ball

- _Ball(aPoint, aNumber)_

Answer a `Ball` with center at _aPoint_ and radius _aNumber_.

```
>>> let s = Ball([0 0 0], 1);
>>> (
>>> 	s.center,
>>> 	s.radius,
>>> 	s.volume
>>> )
([0 0 0], 1, 4/3.pi)
```

